# App Router

## Pages are server components

Do not add `"use client"` to `page.tsx` or `layout.tsx`. Keep pages as server components; interactive UI lives in colocated client modules.

```
app/(auth)/sign-in/
├── page.tsx           # Server — imports form
└── sign-in-form.tsx   # "use client"
```

```tsx
import { SignInForm } from "./sign-in-form";

export default function SignInPage() {
  return <SignInForm />;
}
```

## Route groups

- `(auth)` — public auth (`/sign-in`, `/sign-up`), centered layout
- `(app)` — authenticated, session-checked

## Proxy

Next.js 16 uses `src/proxy.ts` (not `middleware.ts`). Default export `async function proxy()`. Matcher excludes `/api`, `/_next`, `/dev`, static assets.

## Providers

`src/app/providers.tsx` is `"use client"` — TanStack Query / tRPC; imported from root `layout.tsx` (server).
